      "title": "How Shopify Handled 30TB per Minute With a Modular Monolith Architecture ðŸ”¥",
      "url": "https://newsletter.systemdesign.one/p/modular-monolith",
      "date": 1734873324,
      "author": "Neo Kim",
      "unread": true,
      "content": "<p>Get the powerful template to approach system design for FREE on newsletter sign-up:</p><p class=\"button-wrapper\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://newsletter.systemdesign.one/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}\" data-component-name=\"ButtonCreateButton\"><a class=\"button primary\" href=\"https://newsletter.systemdesign.one/subscribe?\"><span>Subscribe now</span></a></p><div><hr></div><p><em>This post outlines modular monolith architecture. You will find references at the bottom of this page if you want to go deeper.</em></p><ul><li><p><em><a href=\"https://newsletter.systemdesign.one/p/modular-monolith/?action=share\">Share this post</a> &amp; I'll send you some rewards for the referrals.</em></p></li></ul><p><em>Note: This post is based on my research and may differ from real-world implementation.</em></p><p>Once upon a time, 3 people decided to sell snowboarding equipment online.</p><p>And set up an e-commerce platform.</p><p>Yet their business model failed.</p><p>So they pivoted to create a software-as-a-service model with the e-commerce platform and called it Shopify.</p><p>Their growth rate was explosive.</p><p>But they wanted to keep it simple and reduce costs.</p><p>So they built Shopify using a classic monolith architecture in Ruby on Rails.</p><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F61a1dee0-5808-4600-9b46-8d47e70613f2_1200x630.gif\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F61a1dee0-5808-4600-9b46-8d47e70613f2_1200x630.gif 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F61a1dee0-5808-4600-9b46-8d47e70613f2_1200x630.gif 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F61a1dee0-5808-4600-9b46-8d47e70613f2_1200x630.gif 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F61a1dee0-5808-4600-9b46-8d47e70613f2_1200x630.gif 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F61a1dee0-5808-4600-9b46-8d47e70613f2_1200x630.gif\" width=\"442\" height=\"232.05\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/61a1dee0-5808-4600-9b46-8d47e70613f2_1200x630.gif&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:630,&quot;width&quot;:1200,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:442,&quot;bytes&quot;:316279,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;modular monolith&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/gif&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}\" class=\"sizing-normal\" alt=\"modular monolith\" title=\"modular monolith\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F61a1dee0-5808-4600-9b46-8d47e70613f2_1200x630.gif 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F61a1dee0-5808-4600-9b46-8d47e70613f2_1200x630.gif 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F61a1dee0-5808-4600-9b46-8d47e70613f2_1200x630.gif 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F61a1dee0-5808-4600-9b46-8d47e70613f2_1200x630.gif 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" loading=\"lazy\"></picture><div></div></div></a></figure></div><p>As time passed, they added features to scale the business.</p><p>Yet it increased the codebase complexity.</p><p>And became difficult to understand &amp; maintain the code.</p><p>So they <em>considered</em> moving to a microservices architecture.</p><p>Although it&#8217;ll temporarily solve their issues, it might create newer problems.</p><p>Here are some of them:</p><h4>1. Infrastructure Costs</h4><p>Each microservice needs a separate deployment pipeline.</p><p>Besides <a href=\"https://systemdesign.one/what-is-service-discovery/\">service discovery</a> and <a href=\"https://www.redhat.com/en/topics/api/what-does-an-api-gateway-do\">API gateway</a> should be set up.</p><p>So it&#8217;ll increase the effort and costs.</p><h4>2. System Reliability</h4><p>There&#8217;s a risk of failure from an <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fallacies_of_distributed_computing\">unreliable network</a>.</p><p>Also security vulnerabilities must be updated in each microservice.</p><p>So it&#8217;ll increase the system complexity.</p><p>Onward.</p><div><hr></div><h4><a href=\"https://bsky.app/profile/systemdesign.one\">This Post Summary - Bluesky</a></h4><p>I wrote a summary of this post (save it for later):</p><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://bsky.app/profile/systemdesign.one/post/3ldvhonfhc22g\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0e3a10c0-8040-458a-abfd-73c47a1a19b3_1404x713.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0e3a10c0-8040-458a-abfd-73c47a1a19b3_1404x713.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0e3a10c0-8040-458a-abfd-73c47a1a19b3_1404x713.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0e3a10c0-8040-458a-abfd-73c47a1a19b3_1404x713.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0e3a10c0-8040-458a-abfd-73c47a1a19b3_1404x713.png\" width=\"1404\" height=\"713\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/0e3a10c0-8040-458a-abfd-73c47a1a19b3_1404x713.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:713,&quot;width&quot;:1404,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:132191,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;Neo Kim Bluesky&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;https://bsky.app/profile/systemdesign.one/post/3ldvhonfhc22g&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}\" class=\"sizing-normal\" alt=\"Neo Kim Bluesky\" title=\"Neo Kim Bluesky\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0e3a10c0-8040-458a-abfd-73c47a1a19b3_1404x713.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0e3a10c0-8040-458a-abfd-73c47a1a19b3_1404x713.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0e3a10c0-8040-458a-abfd-73c47a1a19b3_1404x713.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0e3a10c0-8040-458a-abfd-73c47a1a19b3_1404x713.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" loading=\"lazy\"></picture><div></div></div></a></figure></div><p>And I&#8217;d love to connect if you&#8217;re on Bluesky:</p><p class=\"button-wrapper\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://bsky.app/profile/systemdesign.one&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Follow Bluesky&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}\" data-component-name=\"ButtonCreateButton\"><a class=\"button primary\" href=\"https://bsky.app/profile/systemdesign.one\"><span>Follow Bluesky</span></a></p><div><hr></div><h2>Modular Monolith</h2><p>They wanted the benefits of monolith and microservices architecture.</p><p>But ditch the problems coming with it.</p><p>So they set up a modular monolith.</p><p>Here&#8217;s how:</p><h3>1. Design Principles</h3><p>They designed each module around a specific business domain.</p><ul><li><p>It gave <em>high cohesion</em>.</p></li></ul><p>Think of<strong> cohesion</strong> as grouping functionalities from a business area within a module. Put simply, related functionalities get stored in a specific module.</p><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7c038f8b-bbe0-4325-b335-8c6d60b92b8f_1200x630.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7c038f8b-bbe0-4325-b335-8c6d60b92b8f_1200x630.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7c038f8b-bbe0-4325-b335-8c6d60b92b8f_1200x630.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7c038f8b-bbe0-4325-b335-8c6d60b92b8f_1200x630.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7c038f8b-bbe0-4325-b335-8c6d60b92b8f_1200x630.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7c038f8b-bbe0-4325-b335-8c6d60b92b8f_1200x630.png\" width=\"728\" height=\"382.2\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/7c038f8b-bbe0-4325-b335-8c6d60b92b8f_1200x630.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:630,&quot;width&quot;:1200,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:728,&quot;bytes&quot;:70797,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;High Cohesion and Low Coupling in Modules&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}\" class=\"sizing-normal\" alt=\"High Cohesion and Low Coupling in Modules\" title=\"High Cohesion and Low Coupling in Modules\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7c038f8b-bbe0-4325-b335-8c6d60b92b8f_1200x630.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7c038f8b-bbe0-4325-b335-8c6d60b92b8f_1200x630.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7c038f8b-bbe0-4325-b335-8c6d60b92b8f_1200x630.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7c038f8b-bbe0-4325-b335-8c6d60b92b8f_1200x630.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" loading=\"lazy\"></picture><div class=\"image-link-expand\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container restack-image\"><svg role=\"img\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke=\"#000\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><g><title></title><path d=\"M21 3V8M21 8H16M21 8L18 5.29962C16.7056 4.14183 15.1038 3.38328 13.3879 3.11547C11.6719 2.84766 9.9152 3.08203 8.32951 3.79031C6.74382 4.49858 5.39691 5.65051 4.45125 7.10715C3.5056 8.5638 3.00158 10.2629 3 11.9996M3 21V16M3 16H8M3 16L6 18.7C7.29445 19.8578 8.89623 20.6163 10.6121 20.8841C12.3281 21.152 14.0848 20.9176 15.6705 20.2093C17.2562 19.501 18.6031 18.3491 19.5487 16.8925C20.4944 15.4358 20.9984 13.7367 21 12\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></g></svg></div><div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container view-image\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2\"><polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line></svg></div></div></div></div></a><figcaption class=\"image-caption\">High Cohesion and Low Coupling of Modules</figcaption></figure></div><p>Also they created a <em>public interface</em> for each module and hid the internal logic &amp; data behind it. It let them:</p><ul><li><p>Achieve <em>low coupling.</em></p></li><li><p>Understand the behavior of a module easily.</p></li><li><p>Modify a module without breaking others.</p></li></ul><p>Imagine <strong>coupling</strong> as a measure of dependency between 2 modules.</p><p>A module will always depend on something.</p><p>Yet dependencies must be minimized.</p><p>So they merged modules with many dependencies on each other. (It happens when domain boundaries aren&#8217;t set properly.)</p><p>They designed modules to communicate with each other via public API - function calls. And threw errors if anything got accessed outside the public API.</p><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7ac1ba89-2064-4be8-bd88-2b58a3557b87_1200x630.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7ac1ba89-2064-4be8-bd88-2b58a3557b87_1200x630.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7ac1ba89-2064-4be8-bd88-2b58a3557b87_1200x630.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7ac1ba89-2064-4be8-bd88-2b58a3557b87_1200x630.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7ac1ba89-2064-4be8-bd88-2b58a3557b87_1200x630.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7ac1ba89-2064-4be8-bd88-2b58a3557b87_1200x630.png\" width=\"664\" height=\"348.6\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/7ac1ba89-2064-4be8-bd88-2b58a3557b87_1200x630.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:630,&quot;width&quot;:1200,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:664,&quot;bytes&quot;:76424,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;Modularity vs Deployment Complexity in Architectural Patterns&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}\" class=\"sizing-normal\" alt=\"Modularity vs Deployment Complexity in Architectural Patterns\" title=\"Modularity vs Deployment Complexity in Architectural Patterns\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7ac1ba89-2064-4be8-bd88-2b58a3557b87_1200x630.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7ac1ba89-2064-4be8-bd88-2b58a3557b87_1200x630.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7ac1ba89-2064-4be8-bd88-2b58a3557b87_1200x630.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7ac1ba89-2064-4be8-bd88-2b58a3557b87_1200x630.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" loading=\"lazy\"></picture><div class=\"image-link-expand\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container restack-image\"><svg role=\"img\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke=\"#000\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><g><title></title><path d=\"M21 3V8M21 8H16M21 8L18 5.29962C16.7056 4.14183 15.1038 3.38328 13.3879 3.11547C11.6719 2.84766 9.9152 3.08203 8.32951 3.79031C6.74382 4.49858 5.39691 5.65051 4.45125 7.10715C3.5056 8.5638 3.00158 10.2629 3 11.9996M3 21V16M3 16H8M3 16L6 18.7C7.29445 19.8578 8.89623 20.6163 10.6121 20.8841C12.3281 21.152 14.0848 20.9176 15.6705 20.2093C17.2562 19.501 18.6031 18.3491 19.5487 16.8925C20.4944 15.4358 20.9984 13.7367 21 12\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></g></svg></div><div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container view-image\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2\"><polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line></svg></div></div></div></div></a><figcaption class=\"image-caption\">Modularity vs Deployment Complexity of Architectural Patterns</figcaption></figure></div><p>Each module can be deployed as a separate <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Process_(computing)\">process</a> for fault isolation.</p><p>Yet it&#8217;ll increase <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Serialization\">data serialization</a> costs and network overhead.</p><p>So they deploy every module within the same process.</p><p>And the best part?</p><h3>2. Code Organization</h3><p>They organized code so each module contains a business domain. Put simply, each directory represents a specific business domain. For example, the code for orders and payments modules will be in separate directories.</p><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff457adfd-9298-483a-8d64-1b07505d8c26_586x736.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff457adfd-9298-483a-8d64-1b07505d8c26_586x736.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff457adfd-9298-483a-8d64-1b07505d8c26_586x736.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff457adfd-9298-483a-8d64-1b07505d8c26_586x736.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff457adfd-9298-483a-8d64-1b07505d8c26_586x736.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff457adfd-9298-483a-8d64-1b07505d8c26_586x736.png\" width=\"250\" height=\"313.9931740614334\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/f457adfd-9298-483a-8d64-1b07505d8c26_586x736.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:736,&quot;width&quot;:586,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:250,&quot;bytes&quot;:71349,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;The Directory Structure of a Modular Monolith&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}\" class=\"sizing-normal\" alt=\"The Directory Structure of a Modular Monolith\" title=\"The Directory Structure of a Modular Monolith\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff457adfd-9298-483a-8d64-1b07505d8c26_586x736.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff457adfd-9298-483a-8d64-1b07505d8c26_586x736.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff457adfd-9298-483a-8d64-1b07505d8c26_586x736.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff457adfd-9298-483a-8d64-1b07505d8c26_586x736.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" loading=\"lazy\"></picture><div class=\"image-link-expand\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container restack-image\"><svg role=\"img\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke=\"#000\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><g><title></title><path d=\"M21 3V8M21 8H16M21 8L18 5.29962C16.7056 4.14183 15.1038 3.38328 13.3879 3.11547C11.6719 2.84766 9.9152 3.08203 8.32951 3.79031C6.74382 4.49858 5.39691 5.65051 4.45125 7.10715C3.5056 8.5638 3.00158 10.2629 3 11.9996M3 21V16M3 16H8M3 16L6 18.7C7.29445 19.8578 8.89623 20.6163 10.6121 20.8841C12.3281 21.152 14.0848 20.9176 15.6705 20.2093C17.2562 19.501 18.6031 18.3491 19.5487 16.8925C20.4944 15.4358 20.9984 13.7367 21 12\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></g></svg></div><div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container view-image\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2\"><polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line></svg></div></div></div></div></a><figcaption class=\"image-caption\">The Directory Structure of a Modular Monolith</figcaption></figure></div><p>Also they set up separate database schemas for each module. And avoided transactions across them to avoid coupling &amp; achieve data isolation.</p><h3>3. Benefits</h3><p>A modular monolith is a better way to organize code than a classic monolith. Here are its benefits:</p><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffe244d7f-e342-491d-acd5-1915727d3ef8_727x367.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffe244d7f-e342-491d-acd5-1915727d3ef8_727x367.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffe244d7f-e342-491d-acd5-1915727d3ef8_727x367.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffe244d7f-e342-491d-acd5-1915727d3ef8_727x367.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffe244d7f-e342-491d-acd5-1915727d3ef8_727x367.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffe244d7f-e342-491d-acd5-1915727d3ef8_727x367.png\" width=\"285\" height=\"143.87207702888583\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/fe244d7f-e342-491d-acd5-1915727d3ef8_727x367.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:367,&quot;width&quot;:727,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:285,&quot;bytes&quot;:46152,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;A Modular Monolith Limits the Area of Code Change&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}\" class=\"sizing-normal\" alt=\"A Modular Monolith Limits the Area of Code Change\" title=\"A Modular Monolith Limits the Area of Code Change\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffe244d7f-e342-491d-acd5-1915727d3ef8_727x367.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffe244d7f-e342-491d-acd5-1915727d3ef8_727x367.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffe244d7f-e342-491d-acd5-1915727d3ef8_727x367.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffe244d7f-e342-491d-acd5-1915727d3ef8_727x367.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" loading=\"lazy\"></picture><div></div></div></a><figcaption class=\"image-caption\">A Modular Monolith Limits the Area of Code Change</figcaption></figure></div><ul><li><p>It&#8217;s easier to modify code as the area of code change is limited. (Compared to <a href=\"https://www.baeldung.com/cs/layered-architecture\">layered architecture</a> in a classic monolith.)</p></li><li><p>Developer productivity is high because the codebase is easier to understand.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>There&#8217;s no network overhead because functional calls are enough. (Compared to microservices.)</p></li><li><p>It&#8217;s easier to deploy because there&#8217;s only a single app.</p></li><li><p>The infrastructure costs are low because there&#8217;s only a single codebase.</p></li></ul><p>Besides a modular monolith makes the transition to microservices easier.</p><h3>4. Tradeoffs</h3><p>Each architecture has its tradeoffs:</p><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe2fd1b0c-1608-4769-b28c-a25af5848449_518x392.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe2fd1b0c-1608-4769-b28c-a25af5848449_518x392.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe2fd1b0c-1608-4769-b28c-a25af5848449_518x392.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe2fd1b0c-1608-4769-b28c-a25af5848449_518x392.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe2fd1b0c-1608-4769-b28c-a25af5848449_518x392.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe2fd1b0c-1608-4769-b28c-a25af5848449_518x392.png\" width=\"276\" height=\"208.86486486486487\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/e2fd1b0c-1608-4769-b28c-a25af5848449_518x392.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:392,&quot;width&quot;:518,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:276,&quot;bytes&quot;:51664,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;Horizontal Scaling of a Modular Monolith&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}\" class=\"sizing-normal\" alt=\"Horizontal Scaling of a Modular Monolith\" title=\"Horizontal Scaling of a Modular Monolith\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe2fd1b0c-1608-4769-b28c-a25af5848449_518x392.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe2fd1b0c-1608-4769-b28c-a25af5848449_518x392.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe2fd1b0c-1608-4769-b28c-a25af5848449_518x392.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe2fd1b0c-1608-4769-b28c-a25af5848449_518x392.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" loading=\"lazy\"></picture><div></div></div></a><figcaption class=\"image-caption\">Horizontal Scaling of a Modular Monolith</figcaption></figure></div><ul><li><p>It&#8217;s difficult to scale only a specific module in a modular monolith, so resources might get wasted.</p></li></ul><p>Also failure impact is high because every module runs in the same process.</p><div><hr></div><p>Each architectural pattern solves a specific problem.</p><p>Yet there&#8217;s no silver bullet.</p><p>So the correct solution depends on your needs and scale.</p><p>While Shopify remains one of the largest e-commerce platforms in the world.</p><p>And handled 30TB traffic per minute during black friday.</p><div><hr></div><p>&#128075; PS - Are you unhappy at your current job?</p><p>And preparing for system design interviews to get your dream job can be stressful.</p><p>Don't worry, I'm working on content to help you pass the syste